cat << EOF
This is a Platform Independent Framework for making Internationalized 
Virtual Termial Emulator. Implementing Platform dependent part of this 
Framework, you can easily build Internationalized virtual 
terminal/Widget. This package contains 2 libraries (libiterm, libYiterm) 
and 2 applications (yiterm,fbiterm).

This version is modified for Y-Windows (http://www.y-windows.org/)
